      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Multifunctional Islamic fortified outposts generally reserved for warriors of the Faith who are committed to defense of frontiers and to proselytizing. Multifunctional Islamic fortified outposts generally reserved for warriors of the Faith who are committed to defense of frontiers and to proselytizing.</Note_Text>
